Hi, I’m the head of software in team 5135, our team wants to detect corals this year for the first time and we want advice on what camera should we run the detection on and what software do you recommend using.
our hardware:
we have a raspberry pi 5 with two cameras, one of them is mono and the other is able to detect colors.
we also have a limelight 3g.
we want to know what is best to detect corals reliably and with as little delay as possible.
